name "subsec:Dense-Layer"

\end_inset

Dense Layer
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This is the true implementation of a MLP layer and contains matrix for both
 weights and biases, based on the input dimension and the number of units
 contained in this layer.
 This matrices are initialized with a default method, but there are different
 options from which to choose.
 Even the activation function is set by default but it can be changed.
 There is also the possibility to assign to the layer a regularization parameter
 that can differ from the ones of the other layers.
\end_layout

