\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
On the other hand the dropout layer is a fake layer that only changes the
 input of the successive dense layer zeroing some random inputs.
 It can be initialized with an user selected dropout-ratio and with a specific
 seed for the random generator.
\end_layout

